{#- LLM-facing text is English-only: Cyrillic uses roughly 2–3× more tokens per word.
    This Jinja comment is stripped and never sent to the model.
    Deterministic <task-state> cache for the reasoning prompt and response_observe input.
    Variables: is_empty (bool); subtasks (list of {content_id, text, status, terminal});
               open_count, done_count, cancelled_count (int). -#}
{% if is_empty -%}
No subtasks recorded yet. response_finalize is HARD-GATED on this ledger and will refuse to send a reply while it is empty: lay out the plan with tasks_upsert (new_subtasks) before finalizing. For a trivial answer, add one subtask and mark it done in the same call.
{%- else -%}
Task ledger: {{ subtasks | length }} subtasks ({{ open_count }} open, {{ done_count }} done, {{ cancelled_count }} cancelled).
{% for s in subtasks -%}
- [{{ s.status }}] ({{ s.content_id }}) {{ s.text | replace("\n", " ") }}
{% endfor -%}
{% if discovery_note %}
Discovery: {{ discovery_note | replace("\n", " ") }}
{% endif -%}
{% if next_action %}
Next action: {{ next_action | replace("\n", " ") }}
{% endif -%}
{% if blockers %}
Blocker: {{ blockers | replace("\n", " ") }}{% if allow_finalize_with_blocker %} (allow_finalize_with_blocker set){% endif %}
{% endif -%}
{%- endif %}
